Class Ticket

  • java.lang.Object
    • Ticket

  • public class Ticket
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Mark Class for a flight's tickets containing a unique ticket ID number, passenger info, ticket price with 7% sales tax, Flight number, source, and destination, along with flight time and duration.
